query:
-- Create Contra Costa County agency if not exists
INSERT IGNORE INTO counties (name, state, usesStateProtocols, protocolVersion, createdAt)
VALUES ('Contra Costa County EMS', 'California', 0, '2026', NOW());

-- Get the county ID
SET @ccc_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%Contra Costa%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- Insert Contra Costa County treatment protocols based on their Acid Remap structure
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
-- Adult Cardiac protocols
(@ccc_id, 'AC01', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Adult Cardiac', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Cardiac Arrest. CPR, defibrillation, airway management, and ACLS medications.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AC02', 'Bradycardia', 'Adult Cardiac', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Bradycardia. Atropine, transcutaneous pacing, and dopamine.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AC03', 'Tachycardia - Narrow Complex', 'Adult Cardiac', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Narrow Complex Tachycardia. Vagal maneuvers and adenosine.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AC04', 'Tachycardia - Wide Complex', 'Adult Cardiac', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Wide Complex Tachycardia. Amiodarone and synchronized cardioversion.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AC05', 'Chest Pain/ACS', 'Adult Cardiac', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Chest Pain and Acute Coronary Syndrome. 12-lead ECG, aspirin, nitroglycerin, and STEMI activation.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AC06', 'Post Resuscitation Care', 'Adult Cardiac', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Post Resuscitation Care. Hemodynamic support and targeted temperature management.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),

-- Adult Respiratory protocols
(@ccc_id, 'AR01', 'Respiratory Distress', 'Adult Respiratory', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Respiratory Distress. Assessment and treatment based on etiology.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AR02', 'Asthma/COPD', 'Adult Respiratory', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Asthma and COPD. Bronchodilators, steroids, and CPAP.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AR03', 'CHF/Pulmonary Edema', 'Adult Respiratory', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for CHF and Pulmonary Edema. CPAP, nitroglycerin, and diuretics.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AR04', 'Airway Management', 'Adult Respiratory', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Airway Management. BLS and ALS airway techniques.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),

-- Adult Medical protocols
(@ccc_id, 'AM01', 'Altered Mental Status', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Altered Mental Status. Assessment, blood glucose, and naloxone.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AM02', 'Seizures', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Seizures. Benzodiazepine administration and airway protection.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AM03', 'Stroke/CVA', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Stroke/CVA. Stroke scale, blood glucose, and stroke center transport.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AM04', 'Diabetic Emergencies', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Diabetic Emergencies. Dextrose and glucagon for hypoglycemia.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AM05', 'Allergic Reaction/Anaphylaxis', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Allergic Reaction and Anaphylaxis. Epinephrine, diphenhydramine, and steroids.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AM06', 'Overdose/Poisoning', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Overdose and Poisoning. Naloxone and supportive care.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AM07', 'Behavioral Emergencies', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Behavioral Emergencies. De-escalation and chemical restraint.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AM08', 'Pain Management', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Pain Management. Fentanyl and morphine administration.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW()),
(@ccc_id, 'AM09', 'Nausea/Vomiting', 'Adult Medical', 'Contra Costa County EMS Treatment Protocol for Nausea and Vomiting. Ondansetron administration.', 'https://portal.acidremap.com/sites/ContraCostaCountyEMS', '2026-01-08', 2026, NOW());
